original_title: Honningsvågrevyen: E fortsatt tynn å fin i føtn
overview: The pictures speaks for themselves; after countless miles on the road and thousands of hotdog menus we've achieved the ultimate body. Fat body and skinny legs. Honningsvågrevyen is still making fun of everything; ethnic groups, the royal family, political numbers... maybe you'll even find a parody of yourself. And of course, all of our most familiar characters stops by.
title: Honningsvågrevyen: E fortsatt tynn å fin i føtn
